Get census data for CoE parishes

Source: R/parish_stats.R
parish_stats.Rd

Get 2021 ONS census data for any number of Church of England parishes

parish_stats(nomis_code, parish_codes = NULL, relative = FALSE)

Arguments

nomis_code

The nomis code for the data required must be a length-one character.

parish_codes

Character vector of parishes for which data are desired. If NULL (the default), all parishes are returned

relative

Logical. Should a tibble of relative values be returned? The default is absolute values.

Value

A single tibble

Examples

parish_stats("TS001") |>
